modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod makes the workbench required for almost all crafting. Users will start the game with a workbench and be able to pick up workbenches.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod makes the workbench required for almost all crafting. Users will [start](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-starting-items/) the game with a workbench and be able to pick up workbenches.

Doughphunghus’s fork – updates:

* Mod originally written for A17, likely works with A18.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/doughphunghus/7D2D-Doughs-Khelldons-Mods-a18/tree/main/zzz-Khelldon-GetBenched)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/17197-doughs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Khelldon](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/khelldon/), [Doughphunghus](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/doughphunghus/)
